name: Minecraft-morph-mod-issues
tagline: help i crash when using morph mod
body:
#im using a modded client with these mods(all mods are for 1.7.10):
     1. anti gravity mod(starminer)
     2. applied energistics 2
     3. clockwork phase
     4. code chicken core
     5. dynamic transport mod
     6. enderio
     7. extra utilities mod
     8. ichun util
     9. little blocks
     10. matter overdrive
     11.  minegicka 3
     12. morph beta
     13. nodal mechanics
     14. not enough items
     15. OpenBlocks
     16. OpenModsLib
     17. openperipheral
     18. pneumaticcraft
     19. railcraft
     20. rei's minimap
     21. slimevoid library
     22. thaumcraft 
     23. thaumic tinkerer
     24. transformers
     25. waila
-------------------
In my single player world, every time i try to open the morph menu it crashes my game (it happens on every world not just that one)
i would love some help
oh, and heres the crash report
